The Main Task was to create a responsive magazine website (single page) that contains articles on various topics. The website should be visually appealing and user-friendly and use different CSS concepts. 
  
•	Used semantic HTML5 tags for the structure of the website. 
•	Used CSS Grid Layout to organize the main content of the page.
•	Implemented media queries to ensure that the website works well on different screen sizes and devices.    
•	Used background images and color gradients to give the website an appealing visual design.

